    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tall Windsor armchairs with a horizontal U-shaped armrail and long back spindles crowned by a crest rail curved laterally to follow the outside curve of the seat back.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000014271/Evans, American Windsor Furniture (1989)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sillones Windsor altos con una baranda de brazo horizontal en forma de U y largos husillos de respaldo coronados por un baranda superior curvada lateralmente para seguir la curva exterior del respaldo del asiento.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
